            <div>
                <head>Comments</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5e0001-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:07:32.562+09:00">Stunning example: could be one of the earliest in the Chinese language - if it really means what you say it does, that is.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:11:15.792+09:00">But how can I not speak up on this? is what I think this must mean, no?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.53" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:12:04.026+09:00">don't try to avoid ritual prohibitions</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.55" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:15:18.993+09:00">and bring everyone...</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.58" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:16:53.713+09:00">your bringing up this problem</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.59" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:17:50.137+09:00">Now the bandit's assault on people</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.60" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:18:47.687+09:00">is simply without basis in justice</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.69" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:22:14.156+09:00">In principle</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.76" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:26:49.07+09:00">Ah: the threat!!!</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.80" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-08-21T23:28:47.857+09:00">Don't behave like the hoi polloi who, whenever they feel like saying something go on talking.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.173" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-09-08T23:33:32.111+09:00">and let him consider for himself CH</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.146" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-09-08T23:41:37.152+09:00">So those who will be taken to court on this and will risk losing their lives</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-30a.147" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-09-08T23:42:39.976+09:00">will be more than one person.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_008-3a.253" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-02-18T01:11:40.717+09:00">Wang Ming p. 690, line 11, Vorspann: 天上諸神言；Yu (p. 512) teilt die ganze Passage, die anfaengt p. 688, line 8 (夫三皇五帝。。。), der verlorenen section 220 zu. Barbara Hendrischke.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-2a.208" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T16:59:56.331+09:00">does not attain to the plans/ideas of Heaven</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-5a.56" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T17:01:55.187+09:00">does not accord with the plans/ideas of Heaven</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-29a.1286" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T17:43:00.688+09:00">therefore the did not fall foul of the plans/ideas of Heaven (in action)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-29a.1287" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T17:42:34.424+09:00">and they attained to the spirit of Heaven.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-29a.1914" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T17:47:49.036+09:00">This is to be to independently gain a profound understanding of the plans/ideas of Heaven.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-29a.5173" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T17:49:31.062+09:00">they hurt the human mind</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-29a.5174" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T17:49:53.725+09:00">and fail to accord with the plans/ideas of Heaven.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-29a.5751" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T17:50:51.866+09:00">fear to go against the plans/ideas of Heaven</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-29a.6140" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T17:53:20.287+09:00">those who attain to the plans/ideas of Heaven get to live long</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-29a.6141" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T17:53:13.6+09:00">and those who fall foul of the plans/ideas of Heaven go under.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-29a.6142" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T17:56:21.828+09:00">In principle creatures along with the material world follow regular pattersn</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-29a.6143" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T17:58:55.406+09:00">When a man becomes the king over these things</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-29a.6144" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T17:59:31.369+09:00">and when he becomes a royal superior over other persons,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-29a.6145" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T18:03:12.675+09:00">he must not fail to investigate these regularities and pay particular attention to them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-29a.6206" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T18:08:49.491+09:00">Following one person's pronouncements</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_003-29a.6207" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T18:09:25.471+09:00">is called biased talk.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-21a.135" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T23:32:23.864+09:00">These words are the written text by which manages to attain to the spirit of Heaven.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_006-70a.111" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T23:41:24.983+09:00">desires to continue to act according to the</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-41a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T23:47:55.577+09:00">and follows the plans/ideas of Heaven.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-41a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-19T23:49:56.412+09:00">which just lay in their behaviour</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-44a.154" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-20T10:36:42.858+09:00">is called diverging from the plans/ideas of Heaven</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_007-128a.278" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-20T14:54:05.004+09:00">Does high Heaven love those who have no descendants, and does it not love the living/life?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-19a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-20T15:34:37.642+09:00">Those who emulate Heaven</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5e0001_tls_009-19a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-20T15:35:00.04+09:00">do not fall foul of the plans/ideas of Heaven/</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
